About me

I am a second-year student currently enrolled in the Computer Engineering Program at the University of British Columbia. I am passionate about software development and looking forward to having a career in the technology industry.

With a keen curiosity and an innovative mindset, I am confident in my ability to strive in the industry. I am currently interested in the development of Machine Learning (AI) and API.

My hobbies involve watching movies, cooking, Star Wars and watching/playing football.
